Package camzup.kotlin

Class KtVec2

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Vec2
camzup.kotlin.KtVec2
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Vec2>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Float>
public class KtVec2
extends Vec2
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Float>
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for two dimensional vectors.
